	This file/database contains general information about threat, i.e.
	threat source, threats and scales for measuring threats. It doesn't
	contain any specific threats from real life.

	This is publicly available information taken from NIST 800-30r1.

	The hierarcy, or specializatoin, of threat sources implies inheritance. 
	In other words, if some information source identifies threat source
	coming from adversary, that actually means that this information
	source's threats are equaly valid for all inherited information
	sources.
     
-->

